</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="31" pageNumber="310" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="31.[792,1383,1876,2299]" pageId="31" pageNumber="310">
In the past, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1911" box="[962,1040,1990,2023]" class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Microtus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="31" pageNumber="308" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="eva">C. eva</taxonomicName>
was frequently classified as 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Miller" authorityYear="1896" box="[828,976,2030,2063]" class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Eothenomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="31" pageNumber="310" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Eothenomys</taxonomicName>
. Two subspecies recognized.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="31" pageNumber="310" type="synonymic_list">
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6760419" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6760419" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6760419/files/figure.png" inLine="true" pageId="31" pageNumber="310" startId="31.[793,947,2074,2103]" targetBox="[178,769,1883,2288]" targetPageId="31">
<paragraph blockId="31.[792,1383,1876,2299]" box="[793,1193,2074,2103]" pageId="31" pageNumber="310">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[793,1193,2074,2103]" pageId="31" pageNumber="310">Subspecies and Distribution.</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="31.[792,1383,1876,2299]" pageId="31" pageNumber="310">
<taxonomicName authority="Thomas, 1911" authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1911" box="[796,1139,2113,2142]" class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Caryomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="31" pageNumber="310" phylum="Chordata" rank="subSpecies" species="inez" subSpecies="eva">C.i.evaThomas,1911—-SGansu,extremeEQinghai,SNingxia,NSichuan,SShaanxi,NEChongqing,andWHubei(China).</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
